<title>USA: Jim Hjelm's renegotiates line of credit.</title>
<headline>Jim Hjelm's renegotiates line of credit.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-05-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>Wedding apparel maker Jim Hjelm's Private Collection Ltd said it renegotiated its line of credit with Continental Bank of Garden City, New York.</p>
<p>Under the new agreement, Continental has agreed to reduce its interest payable by Jim Hjelm from four percent above prime to one percent above prime. The company currently has a $1.7 million line of credit from Continental.</p>
